c: 39
v: 5
t: “Adalenga thambo ndi nthaka mwamtheradi. Amakulunga usiku mu usana; ndipo amakulunga usana mu usiku. Ndipo dzuwa ndi mwezi wazichita kuti zitumikire monga momwe afunira. Zonsezi zikuyenda kufikira pa nthawi yake imene yaikidwa. Dziwani kuti Iye (Allah) Ngwamphamvu zoposa; Ngokhululuka kwambiri